---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout 
    title="Agencia de Marketing Digital | SEMTIC" 
    description="Estrategias de marketing digital efectivas para potenciar tu marca, atraer clientes e incrementar tus ventas online."
    image="https://semtic.cl/og-servicios.png">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#2dd4bf] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                Agencia de <span class="text-gradient">Marketing Digital</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                Diseñamos estrategias digitales que multiplican tus ventas y posicionan tu marca en el ecosistema digital.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Beneficios -->
    <section class="py-24 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.3), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                        Impulsa tu negocio al <span class="text-gradient">siguiente nivel</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        No hacemos marketing por hacer. Analizamos tu mercado, entendemos a tu competencia y creamos un plan de acción enfocado en resultados medibles y concretos.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Estrategias personalizadas para tu nicho</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Medición de retorno de inversión (ROI) en cada acción</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#4f46e5] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Transparencia y reportes claros de resultados</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md">
                   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/10 to-transparent opacity-100 rounded-3xl"></div>
                   <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] relative z-10">¿Qué incluye nuestro servicio?</h3>
                   <ul class="space-y-6 relative z-10">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#4f46e5]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5]">1</div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Auditoría inicial profunda</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#4f46e5]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5]">2</div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Creación de ecosistema digital</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#4f46e5]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5]">3</div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Ejecución de campañas omnicanal</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#4f46e5]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5]">4</div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Optimización y escalamiento</span>
                        </li>
                   </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Final -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.95));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                ¿Listo para <span class="text-gradient">crecer online</span>?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                Agenda tu diagnóstico gratuito y descubre cómo podemos ayudarte a alcanzar tus objetivos con nuestra agencia.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/56988169404?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20más%20información%20sobre%20sus%20servicios%20de%20Marketing%20Digital" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#25D366] to-[#3b82f6] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(37,211,102,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Agenda una reunión por WhatsApp
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
